    <info_author>Tim Shadow
ShadowChemosh@yahoo.com

This file is a central place to hold all the weapons as I am starting to need to override lots of weapons.</info_author>
    <info_history><![CDATA[
3/11/2014
-Fixed Claw Blades weapons.

1/19/2013
-Fixed "Eldritch Blast" again to be really fixed this time. Had to add new "Ranged" fields to get the totals to work and feats like Point-Blank Shot.  Hopefully this is the last fix needed.

11/17/2013
-Added "Firearm Bullet & Powder, Crafted" that combines the gun Bullet and Black Powder into a single piece of ammoo to buy. It also has the correct price of 1gp 1sp for a crafted version using the gunsmithing feat.

9/21/2013
-Added in "Claw Blades" weapons.

8/25/2013
-Fixed "Eldritch Blast" timing a little so that Vitrilic Blast can adjust the die size now.

5/25/2013
-"Eldritch Blast" will no longer ever show additional attacks now.  This includes extra attacks from level or Hast spell.

4/27/2013
-Changed "Bane" weapons to be activated to they are easier to use in the iPad app.

9/3/2012
-Changed "Firearm Bayonet, Sword" to be sourced to CoT also.
-Added "Crafted Bullets" and "Crafted Gunpowder".

8/21/2012
-Changed "Firearm, Minotaur Rifle" to be sourced to CoT and to match the new Pathfinder gun changes. Also added in the new HL features for guns.

8/18/2012
-Changed "Crossbow, Minotaur Double" to only be -2 penalty to hit not -4 penalty.]]></info_history>
