  <thing id="wS2Cat9Tai" name="Cat-o&apos;-Nine-Tails" description="A cat-o&apos;-nine-tails, also known as the &quot;captain&apos;s daughter&quot; is a short whip made of nine knotted thongs about 3 feet in length, designed to lacerate and inflict great pain without doing serious permanent damage.\n\nA cat-o&apos;-nine-tails deals no damage to any creature with an armor bonus of +1 or higher or a natural armor bonus of +3 or higher." compset="Weapon">
